D - 
public class XLabeledOp<D extends XDef>
extends XOp

A representation of an XExpr operator parameterized by the label. It is used to represent field/method projection (a.f, a.foo()) when applied to a receiver as part of an XExpr. The specific field/method information is stored in def.
